quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,Twaa-Siin93; iyo ni imirongo ya Qur’an ikaba n’igitabo gisobanutse (kinashyira ibintu ku mugaragaro)
  27,2,(Iyo mirongo) ni umuyoboro ndetse ikaba n’inkuru nziza ku bemera
  27,3,"Babandi bahozaho amasengesho, bagatanga amaturo, kandi bakemera badashidikanya umunsi w’imperuka"
  27,4,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi batemera imperuka, twabakundishije ibikorwa byabo (ibibi bakabibonamo ibyiza), bityo bakaba barindagira muri byo"
  27,5,"Abo ni bo bazabona ibihano bibi (kuri iyi si), kandi ku munsi w’imperuka ni bo bazaba abanyagihombo gikabije"
  27,6,"Kandi muby’ukuri, wowe (Muhamadi)wigishwa Qur’an iturutse kwa (Allah), Ushishoza, Umumenyi uhebuje"
  27,7,"(Wibuke) ubwo Musa yabwiraga umuryango we (igihe yavaga i Mediyana ajya Misri) ati \"Mu by’ukuri, njye ndabutswe umuriro; ndaje mbazanire amakuru yawo (yadufasha kumenya inzira) cyangwa mbazanire igishirira cyaka kugira ngo mwote"
  27,8,"Ubwo yawugeragaho, yarahamagawe (arabwirwa ati) \"Yuje umugisha uri muri uyu muriro n’abari iruhande rwawo; kandi ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, Nyagasani w’ibiremwa byose"
  27,9,"Yewe Musa! Mu by’ukuri, ni njye Allah, Ushobora byose, Ushishoza"
  27,10,"(Allah aravuga ati) \"Ngaho naga inkoni yawe hasi!\"Maze (Musa ayinaze) ayibona yinyagambura nk’inzoka, ahindukira yiruka ntiyagaruka inyuma. (Allah aramubwira ati) \"Yewe Musa! Witinya! Mu by’ukuri,iwanjye intumwa ntizitinya"
  27,11,"Uretse uwakoze ikibi hanyuma ikibi (yakoze) akagisimbuza icyiza. Mu by’ukuri, ndi Nyirimpuhwe, Nyirimbabazi"
  27,12,"Unashyire ukuboko kwawe mu kwaha, uragukuramo kwererana ntacyo kwabaye. (Iki ni kimwe) mu bitangaza icyenda (wahawe ngo ubyifashishe) kwa Farawo n’abantu be. Mu by’ukuri, bo ni abantu b’ibyigomeke"
  27,13,"Ariko ubwo ibitangaza byacu byabageragaho ku buryo bugaragara, baravuze bati \"Ubu ni uburozi bugaragara"
  27,14,"Nuko barabihinyura bidakwiye ndetse baranibona, nyamara imitima yabo ibihamya (ko ari ukuri). Ngaho reba uko iherezo ry’abangizi ryagenze"
  27,15,"Kandi rwose twahaye ubumenyi Dawudi na Sulayimani (Salomo), maze bombi baravuga bati \"Ishimwe n’ikuzo ni ibya Allah, we waturutishije benshi mu bagaragube b’abemera"
  27,16,"Kandi Sulayimani yazunguye (ubuhanuzi, ubumenyi n’ubwami bwa) Dawudi, nukoaravuga ati \"Yemwe bantu! Twigishijwe (kumva) imvugo z’inyoni kandi duhabwa buri kintu. Mu by’ukuri, izini ingabire zigaragara (ziturutse kwa Allah)"
  27,17,"Nuko Sulayimani akoranyirizwa ingabo ze zo mu majini no mu bantu ndetse no mu nyoni, maze zishyirwa mu matsinda"
  27,18,"Kugeza ubwo bageraga mu kibaya cy’inshishi, rumwe mu nshishi rukavuga ruti \"Mwa nshishi mwe! Nimwinjire mu buturo bwanyu, Sulayimanin’ingabo ze batabasyonyora batabizi"
  27,19,"Nuko (Sulayimani) aramwenyura asetswa n’iryo jambo ryarwo,maze aravuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Nshobozagushimira wampundagajeho, inema njye zawe n’ababyeyi banjye, (unanshoboze) gukora ibitunganye wishimira. Kandi unanyinjize mu bagaragu bawe beza ku bw’impuhwe zawe"
  27,20,"Nuko agenzura inyoni maze aravuga ati\"Ko ntabona Samusure? Cyangwa iri mu zidahari"
  27,21,"Mu by’ukuri, ndayihanisha igihano gikaze cyangwa nyibage, cyeretse ninzanira impamvu zumvikana"
  27,22,"Nuko (Samusure) imara akanya gato (iraza), mazeiravuga iti \"Namenye ibyo utamenye kandi nje nturutse i Saba-i (Sheba muri Yemen), nkuzaniye inkuru y’impamo"
  27,23,"Mu by’ukuri,nahasanze umugore (witwa Balqis ari we) ubategeka. Kandi yahawe buri kintu, ndetse afite n’intebe y’ubwami ihambaye"
  27,24,"Nasanzewe n’abantu be bubamira izuba mu kimbo cya Allah. Kandi Shitani yabakundishije ibikorwa byabo (bibi), inabakumira kugana inzira (igororotse), bityo ntibayoboka"
  27,25,"(Shitani yabakumiriye kugana inzira ya Allah) kugira ngo batubamira Allah, we ushyira ahagaragara ibyihishe mu birere no mu isi, ndetseazi ibyo muhisha n’ibyo mugaragaza"
  27,26,"Allah, nta yindi mana ibaho ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri itari we, Nyagasani w’intebe y’ubwami ihambaye"